item.title: RoboForm
item.author: contact@softorage.com (Sanmay Joshi and Softorage contributors)
item.description: RoboForm is a form filler and password manager. Its free version has features such as multi-platform support, unlimited logins, passwords creation, password audit and form filling. Its paid version(s) include features depending on the price paid, such as access on all devices, account data backup, share logins functionality and 24/7 support. Blog I User Manual I Help Center
